name: Rabbit in Wonderland
overview: Once Alice escaped from Wonderland, the maddened queen shut down all the entry doors so Alice could never come back. After a while, the queen discovers that the looking glass is a portal. The queen ordered to destroy all the mirrors in Wonderland but they become crazy and spread all over the land. The queen called the white rabbit, the most agile and fast in the kingdom, to destroy them; but his enemy, the Jack of Hearts wants to sabotage his mission. This failure will cost the rabbit’s head. Enter in Wonderland and help the white rabbit to achieve his mission.
